            bindings = <
        &trans  &trans      &kp C_VOL_UP  &kp C_PLAY  &kp C_STOP          &trans  &trans  &trans  &trans  &trans
        &trans  &kp C_PREV  &kp C_VOL_DN  &kp C_NEXT  &trans              &trans  &trans  &trans  &trans  &trans
&trans  &trans  &trans      &kp C_MUTE    &trans      &trans              &trans  &trans  &trans  &trans  &trans  &trans
                            &trans        &trans      &kp C_PLAY_PAUSE    &trans  &trans  &trans
            >;
        };

